{
  "stem": "13469.6",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then we would cook them and eat them, because they left us no food.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We had no food or water or toilet facilities or anything on the train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But we stopped a lot, and that's when we did everything-- in the fields.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And because the train stopped so often, we could just go further and further away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The engine driver would whistle before he'd go off again kind of thing, and then we could all get back on the train again.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it was sort of like a holiday outing, in a way, come to think of it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We'd go further and further afield, and we'd get into nearby villages.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And there, we would get food off the Germans, either by begging or by stealing or by looting kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And Rudi was to the fore in those sort of activities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As far as I know, we didn't speak to them, because we tended to speak Dutch all the time-- all the time between us, not really German, so no.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we had no relationships with them at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were just trying to get food off them one way or the other, kind of thing, without anything else.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INTERPOSING VOICES]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's interesting you should say that, because one day when I was giving this talk, again-- to Rotary Club, lots of military people-- somebody at the end said, why did you go back to the train?",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was totally flabbergasted by that question.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was something that we never, ever really thought about.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, when we see all these films about [INAUDIBLE] and the Wooden Horse, and all these other escape films, we're wondering what we missed, and why we never tried anything.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
